<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        label {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        textarea {
            height: 200px;
            resize: vertical;
        }
        button:disabled {
            background-color: #ddd;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Edit Page</h1>
        <div class="input-group">
            <label for="title">Title:</label>
            <input type="text" id="title" 
                value="Facts about Lorem Ipsum" 
                placeholder="Enter title here...">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group">
            <label for="content">Content:</label>
            <textarea id="content"   
                placeholder="Enter content here...">Fact 1: Lorem Ipsum is derived from a work by the Roman philosopher Cicero, specifically from his book "De Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" written in 45 BCE.

Fact 2: The text has been garbled and altered from the original Latin, making it nonsensical and perfect as placeholder text for design.
            </textarea>
        </div>
        <button id="saveButton" disabled>Save</button>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
